wpt.name: GC2ZWTY
wpt.desc: Eagleview C&D by Vindicated2287, Traditional Cache (2/1)

groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: Eagleview C&D
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: This cache is slightly smaller than the micro size of a film canister. The GZ is a small turnaround area located in Eagleview just before entering Eagle from 100.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
This cache is not turnpike accessible unless you use exit 312 and take 100 N. Bring your own writing utensil as the cache is only large enough for a log.
Gave this one a difficulty of two only because you may often find that there can be many muggles around if you cache it at the wrong time.

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Quick find after dinner out. TFTC
